video_title: Are you a battery or a vacuum? #shorts #mindset
transcript:
so there's two types of people in this
world there's batteries and there's
vacuums batteries are people when you
spend time with them you feel more
energized you feel excited about your
life you feel motivated and inspired to
do more vacuums are people who suck
energy from you people you can spend
three minutes with them and you feel
like you are completely drained after
being around them if i could give you
the biggest tip it would be find more
batteries and spend more time with them
and get rid of the vacuums in your life
your energy is so important your
community is so important that you need
to realize that if someone's sucking the
energy from you and making you feel
worse about yourself you need to get rid
of them and spend more time with the
people who inspire you and make you want
to be better in this world
